---
// CompanyLogo — the brand's REAL logo rendered MONOCHROME (single-path Simple
// Icons, CC0; fill=currentColor) where available, else the company name as a
// wordmark. Single-color only (BRAND §3/§6 — no rainbow). Trademarks belong to
// their owners; nominative use to denote real alumni employers (golden rule 4).
